	BUYER CONTRACT TO CLOSE		
Assignee	Task	When?	Description
AGENT	Send Ratified contract to TC Team (listings@thinknewman.com)	0 days after Contract Date	
AGENT	Check ratified contract for completeness and accuracy	0 days after Contract Date	Check ratified contract for accuracy, all signatures etc. Send out if not complete, and save if complete
ADMIN	Check ratified contract for completeness and accuracy (2nd)	Immediately 	Check ratified contract for accuracy, all signatures etc. Send out if not complete, and save if complete
ADMIN	Submit for Compliance Review and add to spreadsheet tracker	Immediately	Submit for Compliance Review and add to spreadsheet tracker
ADMIN	Confirm Resale Packet has been ordered by the listing agent 	Immediately 	Confirm Resale Packet has been ordered by the listing agent 
AGENT	Call to client, whats next!	Immediately, either before or after client email goes out 	Call to client, explain what will be happening next 
ADMIN	Send Closing Team Intro Email to Client	Immediately	Send email to Buyer, cc agent
ADMIN	Send Intro Email to all Parties	Immediately	Send email to Co-Op Agent, Lender, and Title to open escrow and provide details/contact info for Buyer(s)
AGENT	Schedule Home Inspection(s) and provide schedule to TC	Immediately	Schedule all inspections with Co-Op Agent if the agent hasn't already scheduled 
AGENT	Order Termite Inspections	Immediately	Schedule all inspections with Co-Op Agent if the agent hasn't already scheduled 
ADMIN	Confirm scheduled HI with LA (Reschedule if necessary)	Immediately	If the requested day and time doesn't work find a better one repeat steps 10-12
ADMIN	Email Client and Listing Agent of Inspection Dates	Immediately 	Email Client and Listing Agent of Inspection Dates
AGENT	Confirm plan to receive EMD	Immediately 	Turn in EMD to Brokerage or Title Co and send receipt to Co-Op Agent
ADMIN	Financing Application Complete Confirmation	immediately	Confirm that a financing application has been completed with the lender (typically done before offer submitted)
ADMIN	MLS - Confirm Buyer's agent is added in MLS and status has been updated	immediately	
ADMIN	Appraisal order confirmation	3-4 days after contract ratification 	Confirm the lender has ordered the appraisal 
ADMIN	EMD receipt FU/Send Receipt to LA 	4 days after ratification 	Follow up to make sure the EMD has been delivered send confirmation/receipt to LA 
AGENT	Review Home Inspection with Buyer(s)	4 days after ratification 	Review Home Inspection results with Buyer(s) and draft Home Inspection Addendum
AGENT	Draft counter-addendum for Home Inspection	4 days after ratification 	If Home Inspection Addendum not acceptable, draft a counter
AGENT	Send counter or signed Home Inspection Addendum to Co-Op Agent	4 days after ratification or at least 1 day before expiration whichever is first 	Send signed Home Inspection Addendum or counter-addendum to Co-Op Agent
ADMIN	Confirm HI contingencies have been removed 	5 days after	Confirm that an agreement between parties has been reached and we are moving forward 
ADMIN	Confirm HI addendum executed	1 day before expiration of the HI addendum 	Confirm that we received the executed addendum 
ADMIN	Save ratified Home Inspection Addendum	1 day after contingency removed 	Save ratified Home Inspection Addendum and upload to file for Broker Compliance
ADMIN	Confirm Title Work has been ordered	7 days after ratification	Complete Title Co Docs and cofirm that an order has been placed 
ADMIN	Check with lender appraisal status	5 days after appraisal completed	Check in on the status of the appraisal, likely won't be back but good to keep us on track 
ADMIN	Appraisal update to buyer/buyer agent- no lender required repairs	would receive from lender when appraisal is complete 2-3wks after ratification (typically)	Provide the update to the BA that appraisal is back at value without repairs 
ADMIN	Appraisal update to buyer/buyer agent- Lender Required Repairs	would receive from lender when appraisal is complete 2-3wks after ratification (typically)	Provide the update to the BA that appraisal and communicate the issues/create the plan to address 
AGENT	Confirm w/ buyer/listing agent how repairs will be handled 	immediately after receiving appraisal w/ lender required repairs 	Will the buyer or seller be responsible for the repairs, check the financing addendum for pre-agreed to lender required repair amount 
AGENT	Schedule repairs with team contractors 	After agreeing on how repairs will be completed 	Reach out to the contractors our team has a relationship with to schedule repairs we are responsible for 
ADMIN	Financing Commitment Complete Confirmation	Two days before the expiration of the financing contingency 	Confirm withh the lender that we have a financing commitment 
ADMIN	Confirm Repairs Made & Request Receipts 	7 days before closing	Confirm with Co-Op Agent or our contractor that repairs are complete and receipts submitted
ADMIN	Send Termite Report./Receipt to Lender/Title Co	7 days before closing 	Send the complete termite report and paid invoice to the lender 
ADMIN	Send Resale Packet & HOA Receipt to Buyer	Immediately after listing agent provides 	Send the HOA resale packet to the buyers for review and discuss the timeline for termination 
ADMIN	HOA addendum executed	2 days after provided to buyer 	Send back the signed HOA Transmittal to the listing agent 
ADMIN	Request Utilities from Listing Agent	7 days before closing	
ADMIN	Send Utilities Info to Buyer	7 days before closing	
ADMIN	Request preliminary ALTA	7 days before closing	Request Closing Docs from Title Co for review
ADMIN	Email Client to confirm requested Settlement and Walk Through Details	7 days before closing 	Email to Buyer asking availability of settlement and walk through
ADMIN	Schedule Closing with Title Company 	7 days before closing 	Schedule Settlement with Buyer(s); Time, day and location
ADMIN	Confirm with Title and Lender about Settlement Details	immediately after scheduled time confirmed	Confirm the buyer requested day time and location is okay with the title company 
ADMIN	Email to LA with Settlement and Walk Through Details	7 days before closing 	Email the closing date and the requested walkthrough date to the listing agent 
ADMIN	Email client confirmed settlement and walkthrough details 	7 days before closing 	Email the client when we have confirmation of the settlement day time and location 
ADMIN	Send a calendar invite to BA and the client for settlement and WT	7 days before closing 	Send a calendar invite to BA and the client for settlement and WT
AGENT	Order Closing Gift 	7 days before closing after financing approval if possible 	Confirm whether or not the buyer's agent needs a closing gift ordered 
ADMIN	Request Final ALTA & Check copies	5 days before settlement 	Save copies of checks & ALTA
ADMIN	Review ALTA and Send to Agent	5 days before closing 	Discuss Closing Docs with Buyer(s) OR schedule time with the lender/title company to review w/ them 
AGENT	Review ALTA with Client 	5 days before closing 	Discuss Closing Docs with Buyer(s)
ADMIN	Confirm w/ lender CD was sent, signed and returned 	3 days before closing 	Confirm w/ lender CD was sent, signed and returned 
ADMIN	Request Home Warranty receipt (If applicable)	3 days before closing 	Request Home Warranty receipt from Co-Op Agent
ADMIN	Confirm Lender clear-to-close	3 days before closing 	Confirm that Lender has issued clear-to-close
ADMIN	Confirm Funds to Close received from Buyers - Email to Title	2 days before closing 	
ADMIN	Submit Commission info in Command Opportunities	0 day before closing 	Enter Commissions into Command Opportunity
ADMIN	Update Think Compass with Closed Date if closing was successful	0 day before closing 	
ADMIN	Scan Checks and save in Google Drive	1 day after settlement	Scan Checks and save in Google Drive
ADMIN	Deliver Check and CD to KWF	1 day after settlement	Deliver Check and CD to KWF
ADMIN	Request Testimonial -	1 day after settlement	Request Testimonial - Google, Facebook and Zillow 
